# MoAA-Prime — MASTER HANDOFF

## What this repo is
MoAA-Prime is a modular multi-agent system (MoE → MoAA) with:
- Agents + contracts
- Router
- Oracle verification
- Swarm deliberation + fusion
- SGM (shared geometric manifold)
- SFC (stability / budget guardrails)
- Duality (Architect/Oracle brain halves)
- Memory: MRE → E-MRE (AEDMC + SH-COS + GFO) integrated later

## Current phase
Phase 1: skeleton + packaging + "hello world" app + smoke tests.

## How to run (once Phase 1 is done)
- Activate venv: source .venv/bin/activate
- Install package: pip install -e .
- Run smoke: pytest -q
- Run CLI: python -m moaa_prime.cli.main hello
